WEBVTT

00:47.600 --> 00:49.130
After what happened today,

00:49.520 --> 00:51.670
we can be certain that Cui Jun

00:53.150 --> 00:54.920
wasn't abducted by Grand Tutor Xie.

00:54.920 --> 00:55.580
Otherwise,

00:55.710 --> 00:57.240
he wouldn't have made a deal with me

00:57.240 --> 00:58.920
just because of a letter from my mother.

00:58.920 --> 01:00.350
If Cui Jun were in his hands,

01:00.350 --> 01:02.150
he could have simply grilled him

01:02.320 --> 01:03.600
for the truth behind
the An and Lu families' case.

01:03.600 --> 01:06.590
I know your little brain
has become much sharper than before,

01:06.590 --> 01:08.050
but it needs some rest now.

01:08.430 --> 01:09.760
Stop thinking about it.

01:16.789 --> 01:17.680
Yummy.

01:20.840 --> 01:22.000
Back when we were on the march,

01:22.000 --> 01:24.200
all we could eat were
flatbreads or dried meat,

01:24.200 --> 01:27.480
and occasionally finding some wild greens
would satisfy our cravings.

01:27.480 --> 01:28.950
Now that you don't have
much of an appetite

01:28.950 --> 01:30.430
and can't eat meat while in mourning,

01:30.430 --> 01:31.830
you could try this first.

01:33.310 --> 01:34.870
I've had wild-green flatbreads before,

01:34.870 --> 01:37.070
but I've never had ones this delicious.

01:37.180 --> 01:39.580
Surely Qing Long couldn't have made these.

01:39.600 --> 01:41.130
Please thank Yan Yue for me.

01:47.430 --> 01:48.120
Okay.

01:52.640 --> 01:54.170
You are Crown Prince Wenxi.

01:54.509 --> 01:56.280
In terms of blood relations,

01:56.840 --> 01:58.150
you should be

01:58.150 --> 02:00.480
the person closest to my mother
in this world.

02:00.480 --> 02:03.010
Emperor Wenxi was my mother's
elder brother,

02:03.200 --> 02:04.590
so you should call her...

02:04.590 --> 02:05.200
Aunt.

02:08.880 --> 02:09.940
But compared to me,

02:10.960 --> 02:13.030
even though you aren't Princess Yunzhao's
biological daughter,

02:13.030 --> 02:14.400
you are her true family.

02:17.470 --> 02:19.600
There's no need for you to tell me that.

02:21.710 --> 02:24.110
Blood ties are merely
where one comes from,

02:24.280 --> 02:25.740
but not where one belongs.

02:27.290 --> 02:29.750
A marriage brought about
by the pressure of the imperial family,

02:29.750 --> 02:31.910
and one that had to be maintained
in order to bind the aristocratic clans

02:31.910 --> 02:33.360
and the imperial family together,

02:33.360 --> 02:36.840
ultimately wasted half the lives of
both Princess Yunzhao and Grand Tutor.

02:36.840 --> 02:38.040
I hope that this time,

02:39.360 --> 02:42.760
you can help Princess Yunzhao
find the freedom she deserved.

02:42.800 --> 02:44.329
You sure sound convincing,

02:44.750 --> 02:47.210
yet you're not exactly any better
yourself.

02:47.680 --> 02:48.240
What?

02:48.680 --> 02:49.590
I mean,

02:51.360 --> 02:52.690
without any witnesses,

02:53.280 --> 02:53.800
how can we bring the murderer

02:53.800 --> 02:55.840
who killed my mother to justice?

02:56.430 --> 02:57.710
Isn't there already a rumor going around

02:57.710 --> 03:00.710
that I killed Princess Yunzhao
to seize the Phoenix Heart Token?

03:00.710 --> 03:02.590
Let's fan the flames.

04:30.600 --> 04:34.530
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

04:34.760 --> 04:37.409
[Episode 18]

04:40.560 --> 04:43.560
Since I harboured prejudices
against the An and Lu families,

04:43.560 --> 04:45.310
I never truly listened to
what was in your heart,

04:44.270 --> 04:47.940
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

04:45.830 --> 04:47.960
thinking it was merely your obsession.

04:47.960 --> 04:51.500
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

04:48.800 --> 04:51.690
I always firmly believed
that you were the one who had wronged me,

04:51.690 --> 04:57.020
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

04:51.950 --> 04:54.830
but I never realized
that I had wronged you as well.

04:56.920 --> 04:58.630
I suspect that 25 years ago,

04:57.659 --> 05:01.100
♪ If the heavens should change
and fate tear me apart ♪

04:59.190 --> 05:01.130
the real Cui Jun had already been killed,

05:01.130 --> 05:05.130
♪ Yet still cannot undo one beat
of my heart's art ♪

05:01.510 --> 05:04.680
and that the man who survived
was a secret agent from Northern Qin.

05:04.680 --> 05:06.750
If that's the case, then perhaps
there's more to

05:05.260 --> 05:08.970
♪ I've traveled so far—
the day I find you again ♪

05:07.510 --> 05:08.990
the An and Lu families' crime
he exposed back then than meets the eye.

05:08.990 --> 05:12.290
♪ I fear you might have forgotten me ♪

05:10.480 --> 05:11.810
He refuses to speak now,

05:12.190 --> 05:13.680
but I've brought him back to Jiankang.

05:12.810 --> 05:15.630
♪ I fear no doom of endless karmic pain ♪

05:15.000 --> 05:16.750
Whether or not I can clear
the An and Lu families' name,

05:15.660 --> 05:18.150
♪ Only that you drift far from my side ♪

05:17.800 --> 05:18.720
at least this time,

05:18.410 --> 05:22.580
♪ Apart from you,
the world is an endless night ♪

05:19.560 --> 05:20.820
I'm standing with you.

05:22.600 --> 05:26.200
♪ Even if my beating heart
wears thin and fades ♪

05:22.720 --> 05:24.380
We were once husband and wife.

05:24.920 --> 05:26.560
May all past grievances be laid to rest,

05:26.450 --> 05:28.220
♪ I'd choose this fate
till death's final line ♪

05:27.920 --> 05:29.680
and may you no longer be trapped
by the past.

05:28.450 --> 05:31.070
♪ I only hope the mortal lands ♪

05:31.100 --> 05:33.760
♪ Can grant our wishes ♪

05:34.020 --> 05:38.260
♪ Through endless night,
let heaven and earth fall apart ♪

05:38.930 --> 05:43.480
♪ Just to gaze upon you one last time ♪

05:43.510 --> 05:44.240
Grand Tutor.

06:02.630 --> 06:04.040
I told you

06:05.870 --> 06:07.330
about Li Mao's background

06:09.000 --> 06:11.800
to warn you about the situation,

06:12.870 --> 06:14.160
not so you could

06:15.240 --> 06:17.310
kill my wife!

06:17.430 --> 06:20.240
You're the one who truly fails to
understand the situation!

06:20.240 --> 06:22.190
Crown Prince Wenxi isn't dead at all,

06:22.190 --> 06:24.650
and they still have
the Phoenix Heart Token!

06:31.830 --> 06:33.000
What did you say?

06:34.360 --> 06:36.620
If Princess Yunzhao had returned alive,

06:36.830 --> 06:39.159
my brother would have had
no chance of survival.

06:39.159 --> 06:40.760
What other option did I have?

06:41.870 --> 06:44.040
I wouldn't spare anyone

06:45.600 --> 06:47.600
who might pose a threat to him.

06:50.430 --> 06:51.360
Grand Tutor.

07:11.310 --> 07:12.040
Mao.

07:19.870 --> 07:20.510
Let's go.

07:33.870 --> 07:35.430
What's this supposed to mean?

07:35.430 --> 07:37.040
I said I'd give you this as a gift.

07:37.040 --> 07:39.240
It's made of black iron,
which is even tougher than refined iron.

07:39.240 --> 07:40.560
It won't rust or corrode for 100 years,

07:40.560 --> 07:44.220
and it's 100 times more powerful
than Eagle King's Longque Blade.

07:47.800 --> 07:49.000
When did you forge it?

07:49.190 --> 07:50.720
Before we left for Guazhou.

07:50.800 --> 07:52.720
But it didn't have a scabbard back then.

07:52.720 --> 07:53.600
I specifically asked

07:53.600 --> 07:54.950
Master Wei from Yunyan Pavilion

07:54.950 --> 07:56.480
to craft one for this sword.

07:56.480 --> 07:57.970
Well? Do you like it?

08:09.630 --> 08:10.480
I'm sure

08:11.390 --> 08:13.920
you wouldn't just give this to me
for nothing.

08:16.560 --> 08:19.680
By the banks of the Qushui River,
there's a mountain called Mount Fengming.

08:19.680 --> 08:21.070
It offers a broad view,

08:21.240 --> 08:22.190
and when the weather is clear,

08:22.190 --> 08:23.800
you can see the rolling mountain ranges.

08:23.800 --> 08:24.930
Behind those ranges

08:25.120 --> 08:26.720
lies my mother's former fief,

08:26.720 --> 08:27.920
Yunzhao Prefecture.

08:28.430 --> 08:32.490
Though, unfortunately, it later
fell under the control of Northern Qin.

08:32.630 --> 08:33.440
So?

08:33.720 --> 08:35.320
So I want to buy this mountain

08:35.390 --> 08:37.270
and make it my mother's burial site.

08:37.270 --> 08:37.960
However,

08:38.150 --> 08:40.440
it is currently owned by
a wealthy local family,

08:40.440 --> 08:41.510
and they're asking for a very high price.

08:41.510 --> 08:43.030
I've scraped together what I can,

08:43.030 --> 08:45.160
but I'm still short by this little bit.

08:46.040 --> 08:48.000
Don't worry, I'm not borrowing it
for free.

08:48.000 --> 08:49.800
I've already paid you interest.

08:50.840 --> 08:52.100
How much are you short?

08:52.200 --> 08:53.400
Five thousand taels.

08:56.270 --> 08:57.320
Don't tell me

08:58.150 --> 09:00.790
that the dignified Heir of Prince Jing'an,
commander of Beifu,

09:00.790 --> 09:01.840
can't even come up with

09:01.840 --> 09:02.900
a mere 5,000 taels.

09:04.240 --> 09:06.440
My father owns a small forested mountain
on the outskirts of the capital.

09:06.440 --> 09:08.150
The fengshui there is no worse than
that of Mount Fengming.

09:08.150 --> 09:09.080
I'd be happy to
gift it to Princess Yunzhao.

09:09.080 --> 09:10.650
If you don't want to lend it, just say so.

09:10.650 --> 09:12.650
Why go to all that trouble with lies?

09:34.030 --> 09:37.830
Your Highness, why did you suddenly decide
to clean the horse today?

09:39.080 --> 09:40.740
Your Highness, it's all here.

09:42.510 --> 09:44.600
You've invested all your personal savings
in the army,

09:44.600 --> 09:46.200
leaving only this small amount on you.

09:46.200 --> 09:47.630
It's only a bit over 3,000 taels.

09:47.630 --> 09:49.150
The dignified Heir of Prince Jing'an

09:49.150 --> 09:51.120
only has 3,000 taels of personal savings—

09:51.120 --> 09:53.380
no one would believe that if word got out.

09:54.080 --> 09:55.210
Sell this red steed,

09:55.750 --> 09:57.670
then exchange all of this for cash

09:58.200 --> 09:59.530
and give it to He Yuanji.

09:59.750 --> 10:01.030
Have her withdraw my entire share

10:01.030 --> 10:02.150
from the family estate

10:02.150 --> 10:03.600
and give it all to Xie Jiayu.

10:03.600 --> 10:05.480
Just tell her it's a loan
from the Prince's household.

10:05.480 --> 10:07.750
But this is the prized Western Regions
steed your father, His Highness, gave you,

10:07.750 --> 10:08.960
1 in 10,000.

10:09.720 --> 10:11.610
You won't find another one like it
in all of Ye.

10:11.610 --> 10:14.670
You wouldn't even bear
to ride it onto the battlefield.

10:29.840 --> 10:30.750
Sell it.

10:37.670 --> 10:39.150
Why didn't you try to talk him out of it?

10:39.150 --> 10:39.880
Why should I?

10:40.150 --> 10:42.720
Everything in this world has a price,
but affection is priceless.

10:42.720 --> 10:44.520
Don't you know what matters more

10:44.870 --> 10:45.630
in His Highness's heart?

10:45.630 --> 10:47.240
Back when he used to toss money
to Master Yuan,

10:47.240 --> 10:48.720
at least you could hear it clink.

10:48.720 --> 10:50.240
Now he doesn't even reveal his name.

10:50.240 --> 10:50.960
You fool.

10:51.510 --> 10:52.480
Can't you think of a way

10:52.480 --> 10:53.610
to let Lady Xie know?

10:54.320 --> 10:55.080
Lady Xie?

10:56.480 --> 10:58.790
I heard that when I was severely injured
after receiving a flogging,

10:58.790 --> 11:00.750
it was Your Highness who paid for
the purchase of precious medicinal herbs

11:00.750 --> 11:01.710
to treat me.

11:02.270 --> 11:04.000
It must have cost Your Highness a lot.

11:04.000 --> 11:05.870
Since I can't pay you back right now,

11:05.870 --> 11:06.960
I offer this deed of debt

11:06.960 --> 11:07.800
as proof

11:08.510 --> 11:10.770
that I'll surely repay the debt someday.

11:12.630 --> 11:13.920
It was merely a small favor.

11:13.920 --> 11:15.200
One should not accept rewards
without merit.

11:15.200 --> 11:17.030
The life-saving kindness Your Highness
has shown me is far too great.

11:17.030 --> 11:18.320
A great favor can become a burden
like an enemy's debt.

11:18.320 --> 11:19.520
I'd rather bear a debt

11:19.630 --> 11:21.830
than carry the weight of your kindness.

11:27.480 --> 11:29.480
Sorry for offending you that day.

11:30.150 --> 11:32.600
The distinction between nobles and commoners
and the differences in people's hearts...

11:32.600 --> 11:34.320
You aristocratic traitors—

11:34.790 --> 11:36.750
you're parasites feeding off our country!

11:36.750 --> 11:38.630
Are not something a woman
like Your Highness could overcome.

11:38.630 --> 11:39.960
I shouldn't have taken my anger out
on Your Highness.

11:39.960 --> 11:42.020
I hereby apologize to Your Highness.

11:46.240 --> 11:47.270
How do you plan

11:48.600 --> 11:50.130
to pay this much money back?

11:51.840 --> 11:53.840
By copying books,
or selling my calligraphy—

11:53.840 --> 11:54.700
I'll find a way.

12:04.270 --> 12:05.000
Let's go.

12:06.150 --> 12:06.840
Qing Long?

12:07.720 --> 12:09.840
Why are you taking the red steed
out of the mansion?

12:09.840 --> 12:11.120
His Highness asked me to sell it.

12:11.120 --> 12:11.720
Sell it?

12:12.270 --> 12:13.790
Yes. His Highness told me
not to say anything.

12:13.790 --> 12:16.520
Please pretend you didn't see it,
Your Highness.

12:31.720 --> 12:32.360
Nanxing.

12:32.790 --> 12:34.250
bring out my short dagger.

12:34.600 --> 12:35.240
My Lady,

12:35.670 --> 12:36.870
but Her Highness

12:37.080 --> 12:38.880
left it to you for self-defense.

12:39.790 --> 12:41.450
I've got no choice. I'm broke.

12:41.670 --> 12:43.320
Take these out and ask around
how much they're worth.

12:43.320 --> 12:45.120
If the price is reasonable,
just pawn them all.

12:45.120 --> 12:47.320
I'll figure out a way to make up the rest.

12:48.600 --> 12:50.200
If we pawn Miraculous Craft as well,

12:50.200 --> 12:51.390
it should probably be enough.

12:51.390 --> 12:54.450
Is His Highness really unwilling
to lend you the money?

12:55.550 --> 12:57.080
That's really stingy of him.

12:57.080 --> 12:59.030
He's the commander of Beifu, after all.

12:59.030 --> 13:01.620
Didn't he just confiscate
the Cui family's mines?

13:01.620 --> 13:03.030
Those were confiscated
on behalf of the court.

13:03.030 --> 13:04.750
They're not
the Xiao family's private property.

13:04.750 --> 13:06.080
Still, I never expected

13:06.440 --> 13:08.790
Xiao Wuyi wouldn't even lend me
5,000 taels.

13:08.790 --> 13:10.450
I thought he would at least...

13:10.670 --> 13:11.360
Xie Jiayu,

13:12.510 --> 13:13.710
I'm smitten with you.

13:14.910 --> 13:16.970
Talking about being smitten with me.

13:17.550 --> 13:18.150
Forget it.

13:18.790 --> 13:20.990
In the end, I only have myself to rely on.

13:24.630 --> 13:25.480
Yuanji.

13:30.240 --> 13:30.720
This is...

13:30.720 --> 13:31.720
I'm lending this to you
on behalf of Prince Jing'an's Household.

13:31.720 --> 13:33.440
Take it and choose any place you like

13:33.440 --> 13:34.550
as Princess Yunzhao's burial site.

13:34.550 --> 13:36.630
The Heir has been fighting battles
all over the country these past years.

13:36.630 --> 13:38.670
Although he hasn't spent much on himself,

13:38.670 --> 13:40.440
Beifu's expenditures have been enormous.

13:40.440 --> 13:42.700
He's poured all his salary into the army.

13:42.870 --> 13:44.120
The expenses of Prince Jing'an's Household

13:44.120 --> 13:46.200
have been completely supported
by me and the Princess Consort.

13:46.200 --> 13:48.550
We truly cannot count on
the Heir and Prince Jing'an.

13:48.550 --> 13:50.630
I oversee
Prince Jing'an's Household's accounts,

13:50.630 --> 13:52.690
and the Heir is indeed short on funds.

13:53.120 --> 13:54.780
I'm being completely honest.

13:55.600 --> 13:57.910
Then where did this money come from?

13:58.340 --> 14:00.460
The Heir had Ferghana horse.

14:01.000 --> 14:03.200
I heard it was a gift from Prince Jing'an

14:03.320 --> 14:04.810
when he won his first battle.

14:04.810 --> 14:07.320
That horse had a pure bloodline
and was priceless.

14:07.320 --> 14:08.550
A few days ago, I saw Qing Long

14:08.550 --> 14:09.810
lead it away to be sold,

14:10.440 --> 14:11.910
along with some land deeds and shop deeds.

14:11.910 --> 14:14.240
All together, this is how much was raised.

14:14.670 --> 14:16.360
The Heir even kept it from me too.

14:16.360 --> 14:18.420
He only told me to send the money over.

14:19.720 --> 14:21.480
Do you know what the two largest expenses

14:21.480 --> 14:23.150
under the Heir's name in the household

14:23.150 --> 14:24.870
were in the past year?

14:25.030 --> 14:25.670
What?

14:25.930 --> 14:28.190
The first was your wedding with the Heir—

14:28.790 --> 14:31.520
a fake wedding doomed to be ruined
from the start.

14:32.480 --> 14:34.390
Well, a fake act has to be made

14:34.390 --> 14:36.870
convincing enough
for people to believe it, right?

14:36.870 --> 14:39.480
The second was the renovation

14:40.240 --> 14:42.390
of this Cangfeng Forge
after you moved into the mansion.

14:42.390 --> 14:43.480
This place used to be nothing more than

14:43.480 --> 14:45.200
an empty room for storing sundries,

14:45.200 --> 14:46.400
abandoned for years.

14:47.360 --> 14:48.360
Didn't you notice

14:48.960 --> 14:51.490
that the furnace outside
was also renovated?

14:55.910 --> 14:56.670
No wonder.

14:57.790 --> 15:00.450
No wonder it looks so much like
the one at my home.

15:13.790 --> 15:14.510
Xiao Wuyi,

15:17.790 --> 15:18.920
you sold your horse,

15:19.080 --> 15:20.940
but you didn't take the interest.

15:22.030 --> 15:22.840
Qing Long...

15:26.200 --> 15:27.150
But this is not

15:31.270 --> 15:32.000
what I want.

15:41.670 --> 15:42.870
What do you want then?

15:52.240 --> 15:53.240
I'm not telling you.

15:53.240 --> 15:54.790
I don't want you to think of this

15:54.790 --> 15:55.790
as a transaction.

16:00.790 --> 16:01.650
Your Highness.

16:01.960 --> 16:04.290
The Empress Dowager is hosting a banquet.

16:05.530 --> 16:06.360
Under what pretext?

16:06.360 --> 16:07.320
She claims

16:08.080 --> 16:09.120
Empress Wenxi

16:09.630 --> 16:10.600
appeared in her dream,

16:10.600 --> 16:13.870
asking Your Highness to bring
the Phoenix Heart Token into the palace.

16:13.870 --> 16:14.600
All right.

16:14.910 --> 16:16.550
She finally couldn't hold back any longer

16:16.550 --> 16:18.080
and came forward on her own.

16:29.480 --> 16:30.240
Mother!

16:31.510 --> 16:32.320
Mother!

16:33.670 --> 16:35.790
Why do people like you, high and mighty,

16:35.790 --> 16:37.480
always try to corner me and my brother?

16:37.480 --> 16:39.150
We simply want to survive.

16:39.630 --> 16:40.490
Your Highness.

16:40.510 --> 16:41.870
My brother has been so kind to Yaoyao.

16:41.870 --> 16:43.790
Why are you still unwilling to let him go?

16:43.790 --> 16:44.750
Calm down!

16:44.750 --> 16:46.410
I never wanted Prince Qi dead!

16:46.550 --> 16:47.720
You hold the Phoenix Heart Token,

16:47.720 --> 16:49.670
and you intend to support
Crown Prince Wenxi.

16:49.670 --> 16:51.000
If he ever makes it to Jiankang,

16:51.000 --> 16:52.600
will my brother
have any chance of survival?

16:52.600 --> 16:53.150
Tell me,

16:53.320 --> 16:55.200
where exactly
is Crown Prince Wenxi hiding?

16:55.200 --> 16:57.030
There's no way I'll tell you that!

16:57.030 --> 16:59.000
Fine. Then let's take this secret with us

16:59.000 --> 17:00.120
and vanish

17:00.480 --> 17:02.000
from this world together!

17:17.240 --> 17:18.000
Mao...

17:20.069 --> 17:20.680
Lejun.

17:22.349 --> 17:23.280
Don't be afraid.

17:26.510 --> 17:27.400
Mao...

17:33.550 --> 17:34.160
Mao.

17:34.960 --> 17:36.110
Do you remember

17:37.790 --> 17:39.030
when we were little,

17:39.720 --> 17:41.850
wandering among displaced refugees?

17:42.590 --> 17:43.510
Back then,

17:44.510 --> 17:46.270
whenever there was a single flatbread

17:46.270 --> 17:47.470
or a bowl of porridge,

17:48.400 --> 17:50.030
you'd always let me have it.

17:55.400 --> 17:57.800
Whenever older children tried to bully me,

17:59.030 --> 18:02.000
you'd risk your life to protect me.

18:02.960 --> 18:04.820
Those memories aren't pleasant.

18:05.030 --> 18:06.490
I've long forgotten them.

18:08.240 --> 18:09.270
But I haven't.

18:11.510 --> 18:13.310
Although those days were harsh,

18:14.790 --> 18:16.350
they were the happiest time

18:17.370 --> 18:18.410
of my life.

18:19.640 --> 18:21.590
Because even back then,

18:22.350 --> 18:25.400
I knew I had the best older brother
in the entire world—

18:30.030 --> 18:31.830
one who'd never let go of my hand,

18:32.920 --> 18:34.640
not even in death.

18:36.110 --> 18:36.920
Mao.

18:38.440 --> 18:40.000
I wasn't afraid then,

18:41.070 --> 18:42.830
and I'm even less afraid now.

18:43.750 --> 18:44.440
Mao.

18:46.160 --> 18:48.090
I will protect you, no matter what.

18:58.750 --> 18:59.640
It's alright.

19:00.270 --> 19:01.200
Don't be afraid.

19:17.000 --> 19:17.590
Yaoyao.

19:19.070 --> 19:20.870
Greetings, Princess Pingning.

19:24.880 --> 19:25.440
Yaoyao.

19:26.000 --> 19:27.350
Are you truly determined

19:27.350 --> 19:28.750
to draw a line between us?

19:29.910 --> 19:30.680
Her Highness...

19:30.680 --> 19:32.270
Other than an admission of guilt,

19:32.270 --> 19:33.680
I never want to hear another word

19:33.680 --> 19:35.410
about my mother from your lips.

19:35.880 --> 19:37.340
We were once good friends.

19:37.960 --> 19:40.960
There's no need for
such hollow pretenses between us.

19:45.160 --> 19:45.960
Yaoyao.

19:48.030 --> 19:49.290
You've truly grown up.

19:49.920 --> 19:52.320
It's all because of you
that I had to grow up.

19:52.720 --> 19:53.790
Do you really think

19:53.790 --> 19:55.250
your scheme was flawless?

19:56.310 --> 19:57.110
That day,

19:58.270 --> 20:00.400
Her Highness and I
both fell off the cliff.

20:00.400 --> 20:02.030
If not for a tree that caught me,

20:02.030 --> 20:03.750
I wouldn't have survived, either.

20:03.750 --> 20:06.010
And it was Young Lord Xiao's men saved me.

20:07.110 --> 20:09.030
M-My hand had only just healed.

20:09.400 --> 20:12.000
To accuse me of
trying to harm Princess Yunzhao

20:12.850 --> 20:14.110
is rather absurd.

20:14.510 --> 20:15.570
If that's the case,

20:16.590 --> 20:18.350
then why did you have Da
snatch the coachman's family

20:18.350 --> 20:19.880
from me?

20:20.790 --> 20:21.590
Were you afraid

20:21.590 --> 20:24.250
they witnessed something
they shouldn't have?

20:27.960 --> 20:29.620
But they didn't see anything.

20:34.920 --> 20:35.550
Lejun.

20:36.480 --> 20:38.160
I truly hope it wasn't you.

20:39.030 --> 20:40.030
Because if it was,

20:40.400 --> 20:43.000
I'd be deeply disappointed
in our friendship.

20:43.720 --> 20:44.400
Yaoyao.

20:50.480 --> 20:52.750
I didn't expect you
to enter the palace today.

20:52.750 --> 20:53.440
Mao.

20:54.160 --> 20:55.070
You knew I was using you

20:55.070 --> 20:56.030
to test Li Lejun.

20:56.680 --> 20:57.740
She's your sister.

20:58.160 --> 21:00.350
I believe you only learned about it
afterwards.

21:00.350 --> 21:02.640
I understand that
you were put in a difficult position.

21:02.640 --> 21:03.640
I don't blame you.

21:04.320 --> 21:07.850
But please, don't make things difficult
for me anymore either.

21:55.510 --> 21:57.400
Long live Your Majesty!

21:57.590 --> 21:58.830
You may rise, my beloved ministers.

21:58.830 --> 22:00.480
Thank you, Your Majesty!

22:03.440 --> 22:05.170
Today, at this palace banquet,

22:05.200 --> 22:08.260
I'd like to raise a toast with
all my beloved ministers.

22:16.750 --> 22:19.480
A few days ago, Empress Wenxi
appeared to me in a dream,

22:19.480 --> 22:20.750
and I've learned
that the old prophecy—

22:20.750 --> 22:23.240
"when the Phoenix Heart Tokens appear,
peace shall be restored in the world"—

22:23.240 --> 22:24.200
is no mere tale.

22:24.640 --> 22:25.940
Two Phoenix Heart Tokens have been

22:25.940 --> 22:29.200
passed down to Princess Yunzhao
and Cui Jun respectively.

22:33.750 --> 22:34.610
That's enough.

22:37.790 --> 22:38.480
My Lord,

22:39.400 --> 22:41.070
what's the point of arresting me?

22:41.070 --> 22:42.680
I'm a useless wreck now.

22:43.160 --> 22:46.510
The Phoenix Heart Token
is in Xiao Wuyi's hands.

22:48.000 --> 22:48.930
Young Lord Xiao.

22:49.400 --> 22:51.510
It's been quite some time
since you returned from Guazhou.

22:51.510 --> 22:55.110
When will the convicted criminal Cui
be transferred to the Court of Judicial Review?

22:55.110 --> 22:57.310
And where is the Phoenix Heart Token?

22:58.030 --> 22:58.830
Your Majesty.

22:59.310 --> 23:01.510
Cui Jun was abducted.

23:03.510 --> 23:04.710
When did this happen?

23:04.750 --> 23:06.240
And where was he abducted?

23:08.850 --> 23:09.780
It was 5 days ago.

23:10.110 --> 23:11.200
I'm still searching for him.

23:11.200 --> 23:12.570
He was abducted 5 days ago,

23:12.570 --> 23:13.960
so why didn't you report it?

23:13.960 --> 23:16.000
Do you have any regard for the laws of Ye?

23:16.000 --> 23:16.830
Or could it be that

23:16.830 --> 23:18.490
you hid Cui Jun away yourself—

23:18.510 --> 23:20.790
just like how you silenced
Princess Yunzhao

23:20.790 --> 23:22.400
and stole her Phoenix Heart Token?

23:22.400 --> 23:24.510
Vice Minister Qi, you seem eager
to pin a crime on me.

23:24.510 --> 23:26.350
I have long submitted a memorial
confessing my fault

23:26.350 --> 23:28.080
over Cui Jun's disappearance.

23:28.240 --> 23:31.500
Deliver this memorial to
the Department of State Affairs.

23:31.640 --> 23:34.240
Remember, slip it in
among the daily greetings memorials

23:34.240 --> 23:35.110
so it draws no attention.

23:35.110 --> 23:35.840
Understood.

23:36.590 --> 23:38.590
I know the Cui Family Case
is of great importance,

23:38.590 --> 23:41.000
but I haven't heard anything
from the Department of State Affairs.

23:41.000 --> 23:42.330
I was wondering myself—

23:42.550 --> 23:43.750
how is it that Cui Jun has disappeared,

23:43.750 --> 23:45.270
yet the court doesn't seem concerned
at all?

23:45.270 --> 23:46.880
As a witness in the Cui Family Case,

23:46.880 --> 23:49.480
I've been waiting for
the court deliberation.

23:49.880 --> 23:50.880
Vice Minister Qi.

23:50.880 --> 23:53.160
You've gone and accused me of
silencing Princess Yunzhao.

23:53.160 --> 23:54.560
Do you have any evidence?

23:54.890 --> 23:56.270
Might I charge you with
lodging a false accusation?

23:56.270 --> 23:56.790
You...

23:58.440 --> 24:00.070
Anyway, Cui Jun disappeared
while he was in your custody.

24:00.070 --> 24:03.200
Enough. You are both
loyal and righteous ministers.

24:03.200 --> 24:04.350
There is no need to blame each other.

24:04.350 --> 24:05.680
Your Majesty, what I mean is that

24:05.680 --> 24:07.960
Young Lord Xiao deliberately concealed
the Phoenix Heart Token's whereabouts.

24:07.960 --> 24:09.550
Now that Princess Yunzhao fell dead

24:09.550 --> 24:10.920
and Cui Jun has disappeared
without a trace,

24:10.920 --> 24:13.000
if it weren't for Empress Wenxi
appearing to you in a dream,

24:13.000 --> 24:13.960
we would all

24:13.960 --> 24:15.620
remain kept in the dark by him.

24:15.640 --> 24:17.700
I believe there's definitely more to

24:17.830 --> 24:20.310
Princess Yunzhao's death
than meets the eye.

24:20.310 --> 24:23.550
I respectfully request that Your Majesty
conduct a thorough investigation.

24:23.550 --> 24:24.480
Grand Tutor Xie.

24:24.590 --> 24:25.400
Since Vice Minister Qi insists

24:25.400 --> 24:27.110
there's more to Princess Yunzhao's death,

24:27.110 --> 24:29.070
would you support a thorough investigation

24:29.070 --> 24:31.200
to seek justice for Princess Yunzhao?

24:33.880 --> 24:35.080
If there is evidence,

24:35.830 --> 24:38.230
then naturally it should be investigated.

24:38.440 --> 24:39.550
Since this is merely an accusation

24:39.550 --> 24:40.550
with no evidence,

24:40.880 --> 24:43.940
let's put the matter of Princess Yunzhao
aside for now.

24:44.110 --> 24:45.040
Young Lord Xiao.

24:46.160 --> 24:48.400
Do you have Cui Jun's Phoenix Heart Token
in your possession?

24:48.400 --> 24:50.260
Don't tell me it was snatched away

24:50.400 --> 24:52.600
along with Cui Jun when he was abducted.

24:53.070 --> 24:53.870
No, it wasn't.

24:54.200 --> 24:55.530
The Phoenix Heart Token

24:56.070 --> 24:57.600
is indeed in my possession.

25:00.510 --> 25:01.970
So it's in his possession?

25:05.750 --> 25:07.550
Is that the Phoenix Heart Token?

25:13.030 --> 25:14.480
Everyone, please take a look.

25:14.480 --> 25:16.310
This is the Phoenix Heart Token
that Cui Jun had.

25:16.310 --> 25:18.240
So this is the Phoenix Heart Token?

25:19.000 --> 25:21.030
I wonder if when Empress Wenxi
appeared in your dream,

25:21.030 --> 25:23.690
was this the piece she showed you,
Your Majesty?

25:27.030 --> 25:28.920
Since you all wish to see it so badly,

25:28.920 --> 25:30.180
why not pass it around?

25:39.070 --> 25:41.350
It doesn't seem all that special.

25:42.200 --> 25:44.310
Isn't this just an ordinary token?
How could it deserve the saying

25:44.310 --> 25:48.000
"when the Phoenix Heart Tokens appear,
peace shall be restored in the world"?

25:48.000 --> 25:50.350
It is said the Cui family's private mines

25:50.960 --> 25:53.960
were discovered
because of this Phoenix Heart Token.

26:08.240 --> 26:09.400
In your opinion, Young Lord Xiao,

26:09.400 --> 26:11.070
after Cui Jun has finally been
brought to justice

26:11.070 --> 26:15.670
after having committed
countless crimes,
who should this Token be handed over to?

26:22.270 --> 26:24.050
Did Empress Wenxi not mention this

26:24.050 --> 26:26.000
to Your Majesty when she appeared
in your dream?

26:26.000 --> 26:27.110
"Under Heaven,

26:27.440 --> 26:29.090
all land belongs to the ruler;

26:29.090 --> 26:30.170
within the realm,

26:30.270 --> 26:31.640
all people are the ruler's subjects.

26:31.640 --> 26:34.100
Yet unfair divisions burden the officials,

26:38.200 --> 26:40.000
while I alone toil tirelessly.

26:45.590 --> 26:47.110
Praise that I am not yet worn with age,

26:47.110 --> 26:48.640
still strong and vigorous.

26:48.800 --> 26:51.920
With robust strength,
I oversee all corners of the realm."

26:51.920 --> 26:53.750
I hope Your Majesty will have sympathy for
the Beifu troops

26:53.750 --> 26:55.400
who fight without regard for their lives,

26:55.400 --> 26:57.260
yet suffer from shoddy weaponry.

26:57.480 --> 26:58.510
I respectfully request
that the copper and iron mines

26:58.510 --> 27:00.790
confiscated from
the Cui family's private mines

27:00.790 --> 27:02.450
be allocated to the Beifu Army

27:02.480 --> 27:04.080
to upgrade their armaments.

27:06.480 --> 27:08.140
Please rise, Young Lord Xiao.

27:09.880 --> 27:11.880
What you speak makes perfect sense.

27:12.550 --> 27:14.920
The Beifu soldiers are warriors
of our great Ye.

27:14.920 --> 27:17.270
I approved your Beifu Reform

27:17.310 --> 27:20.110
precisely to forge
a more elite, formidable army.

27:20.440 --> 27:23.170
Moreover, you've rendered
meritorious service

27:23.310 --> 27:25.000
in cracking the Cui Family Case
and deserve a reward.

27:25.000 --> 27:26.480
I find your request

27:27.310 --> 27:28.310
most reasonable.

27:28.480 --> 27:31.410
The Cui family's private mines
shall be dedicated to

27:31.960 --> 27:34.090
upgrading the Beifu Army's weaponry.

27:36.830 --> 27:38.630
On behalf of the Beifu soldiers,

27:38.640 --> 27:41.300
I thank Your Majesty for
your benevolent grace.

27:44.310 --> 27:45.200
Xiao Wuyi!

27:46.310 --> 27:47.530
How dare you mock me?

27:48.160 --> 27:49.350
Where's the Phoenix Heart Token?

27:49.350 --> 27:50.240
How could this be?

27:50.240 --> 27:51.270
How come it's empty?

27:51.270 --> 27:52.160
I have no idea.

27:52.720 --> 27:53.440
The Phoenix Heart Token

27:53.440 --> 27:55.440
was right here in this brocade box
just moments ago.

27:55.440 --> 27:57.500
All the officials in the court saw it.

27:57.790 --> 27:58.750
-Yeah, we all saw it.
-How could it be gone?

27:58.750 --> 27:59.680
There's no way.

27:59.680 --> 28:00.240
Exactly.

28:07.070 --> 28:09.040
Everyone saw it.
It needs to be thoroughly investigated.

28:09.040 --> 28:09.870
Your Majesty.

28:10.440 --> 28:11.590
I noticed

28:11.840 --> 28:13.970
that when His Highness turned around,

28:14.070 --> 28:16.510
Princess Pingning
stole the Phoenix Heart Token.

28:16.510 --> 28:18.400
I didn't! You're slandering me!

28:18.590 --> 28:20.830
Doing that in front of everyone here—
do you think I'm crazy?

28:20.830 --> 28:23.760
Whether you have it or not,
we'll know after a search.

28:25.090 --> 28:25.770
Search her.

28:28.240 --> 28:29.040
Your Majesty!

28:30.880 --> 28:31.680
I didn't...

28:32.640 --> 28:33.750
I didn't. I...

28:35.590 --> 28:37.520
It was really on her. It really was.

28:38.720 --> 28:39.520
Your Majesty!

28:39.750 --> 28:41.680
Your Majesty, that's impossible!

28:41.960 --> 28:43.170
I was framed.

28:43.200 --> 28:44.270
I-I didn't take it!

28:56.960 --> 28:57.760
Your Majesty.

28:58.680 --> 29:00.510
May I borrow the brocade box?

29:01.200 --> 29:01.790
Granted.

29:15.680 --> 29:17.410
There's a hidden compartment?

29:19.110 --> 29:19.590
You...

29:19.750 --> 29:20.550
That's right.

29:20.830 --> 29:22.630
You didn't take Cui Jun's token.

29:23.070 --> 29:25.000
Because the one that fell out of you

29:25.400 --> 29:26.510
was my mother's.

29:28.160 --> 29:29.360
Princess Yunzhao's?

29:31.590 --> 29:32.920
Why did she have
Princess Yunzhao's token?

29:32.920 --> 29:33.510
Exactly.

29:34.440 --> 29:35.680
Please forgive me, Your Majesty,

29:35.680 --> 29:37.590
for contriving this contraption
to conceal the Phoenix Heart Token

29:37.590 --> 29:38.480
and deceiving you.

29:38.480 --> 29:40.880
I did so only to retrieve the token
on Princess Pingning

29:40.880 --> 29:43.540
and uncover the truth
behind my mother's death.

29:45.680 --> 29:46.640
I'm innocent.

29:47.000 --> 29:49.550
That Phoenix Heart Token
didn't belong to Princess Yunzhao.

29:49.550 --> 29:50.800
What makes you say so?

29:51.550 --> 29:54.150
Could it be that
you've seen my mother's token?

29:54.150 --> 29:54.910
When?

30:07.510 --> 30:08.200
Li Lejun.

30:09.110 --> 30:11.270
You murdered Princess Yunzhao
for the Phoenix Heart Token.

30:11.270 --> 30:12.480
The Phoenix Heart Token on you

30:12.480 --> 30:13.880
is the most compelling evidence
of your guilt.

30:13.880 --> 30:14.940
It's not like that.

30:15.590 --> 30:16.250
It's not...

30:18.070 --> 30:19.200
It seems

30:19.920 --> 30:22.650
Princess Yunzhao's death
is indeed suspicious.

30:25.070 --> 30:25.920
It's fake.

30:26.240 --> 30:27.810
That Phoenix Heart Token is fake.

30:27.810 --> 30:29.420
It was forged, Your Majesty!

30:29.640 --> 30:30.480
Your Majesty.

30:31.350 --> 30:32.960
I've heard that the Phoenix Heart Tokens

30:32.960 --> 30:34.830
were cast from the Phoenix Imperial Seal

30:34.830 --> 30:35.830
of Empress Wenxi.

30:36.070 --> 30:37.440
Though the carvings can be replicated,

30:37.440 --> 30:38.310
the unique material of
the Phoenix Imperial Seal

30:38.310 --> 30:39.400
cannot be faked.

30:40.070 --> 30:41.400
Whether it's genuine or not,

30:41.400 --> 30:44.200
we need only compare
the two Phoenix Heart Tokens.

30:54.040 --> 30:56.280
Cui Jun's, Prince Jing'an's.

30:57.220 --> 30:58.350
And this one...

31:04.350 --> 31:06.550
This one belongs to Crown Prince Wenxi.

31:08.000 --> 31:09.060
The engraving on it

31:09.480 --> 31:11.280
was carved by my mother herself.

31:13.110 --> 31:15.170
This one is the "Phoenix Head" token.

31:16.000 --> 31:19.060
It holds command over
the other 3 Phoenix Heart Tokens.

31:19.270 --> 31:21.880
Are you truly willing to take out
one of the tokens

31:21.880 --> 31:23.680
to play along with me in this act?

31:23.680 --> 31:24.550
Right now, the world only knows of

31:24.550 --> 31:26.790
the 2 tokens held by
Cui Jun and my mother.

31:26.790 --> 31:28.920
They have no idea
that the rest are in your possession.

31:28.920 --> 31:29.980
Once you reveal it,

31:30.510 --> 31:32.790
at the very least Grand Tutor and Li Mao
will learn that

31:32.790 --> 31:34.990
Prince Jing'an was also a token holder.

31:35.510 --> 31:36.460
Your identity

31:37.310 --> 31:38.310
might be exposed.

31:39.680 --> 31:41.060
What goes around comes around.

31:41.060 --> 31:43.000
Debts of gratitude and vengeance
must be repaid.

31:43.000 --> 31:44.600
It's just a token, after all.

31:44.750 --> 31:46.950
If it can bring the murderer to justice,

31:47.390 --> 31:48.450
then it's worth it.

31:52.880 --> 31:54.110
It's indeed genuine.

31:56.920 --> 31:58.110
No way.

31:59.270 --> 32:00.510
No way...

32:04.030 --> 32:04.920
It was you.

32:05.680 --> 32:08.410
Xiao Wuyi, so you also have
a Phoenix Heart Token.

32:09.770 --> 32:10.900
Princess Pingning,

32:11.790 --> 32:13.250
what do you mean by "also"?

32:14.200 --> 32:16.130
That Phoenix Heart Token is yours.

32:16.160 --> 32:17.510
You used your own token

32:17.540 --> 32:19.030
to help Jiayu frame me.

32:21.350 --> 32:22.070
Princess Pingning,

32:22.070 --> 32:24.930
do you truly think I, Xiao Wuyi,
am some kind of saint

32:25.440 --> 32:26.570
Everyone knows that

32:26.640 --> 32:29.350
the Phoenix Heart Tokens contain secrets
about hidden mineral deposits.

32:29.350 --> 32:30.950
Tell me, which one of you here

32:31.000 --> 32:32.130
would not want them?

32:32.750 --> 32:34.410
If I had a Phoenix Heart Token,

32:34.550 --> 32:35.680
why wouldn't I keep it hidden

32:35.680 --> 32:37.200
and secretly mine the resources?

32:37.200 --> 32:39.160
Why would I bring it out
in front of all the court officials

32:39.160 --> 32:40.400
just to frame you?

32:40.720 --> 32:42.050
Who do you think you are?

32:43.000 --> 32:44.510
I'd like to ask all of you present:

32:44.510 --> 32:45.680
does anyone truly believe I, Xiao Wuyi,

32:45.680 --> 32:47.610
would be so selfless and generous?

32:50.350 --> 32:52.510
Your Majesty,
besides the Phoenix Heart Token,

32:52.510 --> 32:53.710
I also have a witness.

32:54.920 --> 32:55.650
Summon them.

33:03.160 --> 33:05.270
This is Ms. Yang, the coachman's wife.

33:05.270 --> 33:06.930
They saw nothing to begin with

33:07.400 --> 33:08.790
and were no witnesses at all.

33:08.790 --> 33:10.440
But after you abducted them,

33:10.880 --> 33:13.480
they ended up becoming witnesses
against you.

33:14.110 --> 33:14.750
She...

33:15.110 --> 33:16.880
She asked me where I was

33:17.240 --> 33:19.440
between 3 to 4 a.m.
on the day of the incident,

33:19.440 --> 33:21.110
and whether I had been to the stable.

33:21.110 --> 33:22.680
After learning that
I had not yet gotten up,

33:22.680 --> 33:23.920
she asked no further questions.

33:23.920 --> 33:25.640
That must've been the very hour
you snuck into the stables

33:25.640 --> 33:27.300
to slip the poison, wasn't it?

33:31.030 --> 33:31.750
Let's go.

33:41.340 --> 33:42.010
Wait.

33:45.310 --> 33:47.040
Don't commit any more killing.

34:01.350 --> 34:03.350
I really should've killed them all.

34:04.310 --> 34:06.030
Princess Pingning murdered my mother

34:06.030 --> 34:07.890
to seize the Phoenix Heart Token.

34:08.440 --> 34:11.170
Please seek justice for my mother,
Your Majesty.

34:13.360 --> 34:13.920
Your Majesty.

34:13.920 --> 34:15.710
These pieces of evidence are not enough
to convict Lejun.

34:15.710 --> 34:16.960
Further investigation is needed.

34:16.960 --> 34:18.440
Please deliberate this matter
with caution, Your Majesty.

34:18.440 --> 34:19.840
Prince Qi, are you trying

34:20.070 --> 34:22.000
to cover up for Princess Pingning?

34:31.630 --> 34:34.030
If Princess Pingning truly feels wronged,

34:34.550 --> 34:38.190
we might as well have the entire
Eastern Palace thoroughly searched

34:38.190 --> 34:39.670
to prove her innocence.

34:44.400 --> 34:45.199
Your Majesty.

34:45.330 --> 34:46.530
-Your Majesty!
-I...

34:48.150 --> 34:49.010
I plead guilty.

34:49.550 --> 34:49.840
Lejun!

34:49.840 --> 34:50.699
I plead guilty.

34:51.960 --> 34:52.630
It was me.

34:54.190 --> 34:56.150
I murdered Princess Yunzhao

34:56.510 --> 34:58.370
to seize her Phoenix Heart Token.

35:11.150 --> 35:12.950
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

35:15.880 --> 35:16.550
He Tian.

35:16.550 --> 35:17.360
Guards.

35:23.800 --> 35:24.630
That day,

35:25.550 --> 35:28.280
you suddenly had a stomachache
and needed to lie down.

35:28.280 --> 35:29.880
I was the one who drugged you.

35:31.900 --> 35:32.700
What's wrong?

35:33.280 --> 35:33.920
Mother,

35:34.070 --> 35:35.330
I feel a little unwell.

35:36.070 --> 35:38.480
Your Highness,
why don't we share a ride?

35:39.150 --> 35:40.630
I spared you

35:41.150 --> 35:43.810
only because I did not wish
to drag you into this.

35:44.110 --> 35:45.710
If I had been ruthless enough

35:46.480 --> 35:50.140
to strike directly at your carriage
with Princess Yunzhao inside

35:50.400 --> 35:52.330
and send both of you to your deaths,

35:56.590 --> 35:59.320
none of this would have happened today,
would it?

36:08.670 --> 36:09.280
Lejun!

36:49.670 --> 36:50.470
Your Majesty.

36:51.590 --> 36:53.630
Princess Yunzhao did not die
as a criminal.

36:53.630 --> 36:54.440
This token

36:54.600 --> 36:56.400
was left to her by Empress Wenxi.

36:57.110 --> 36:58.360
Now that she's passed away

36:58.360 --> 36:59.920
and had divorced Grand Tutor Xie,

36:59.920 --> 37:00.800
this token

37:01.480 --> 37:04.110
should rightfully be inherited
by her offspring.

37:04.110 --> 37:06.240
So, according to you, Young Lord Xiao,

37:06.280 --> 37:07.550
-we should...
-The whereabouts of the remaining

37:07.550 --> 37:09.800
Phoenix Heart Tokens are still unknown.

37:09.800 --> 37:11.840
If Your Majesty were to claim them
all for yourself

37:11.840 --> 37:13.670
in front of the entire court,

37:13.670 --> 37:15.710
I'm afraid the remaining token holders

37:15.710 --> 37:17.170
would never come forward.

37:20.150 --> 37:23.350
As for whether it should go to
Grand Tutor Xie or Xie Jiayu—

37:23.480 --> 37:25.140
the choice is Your Majesty's.

37:35.030 --> 37:36.280
Come to me.

37:46.280 --> 37:47.360
Good girl.

37:48.280 --> 37:50.140
You've really been through a lot.

37:51.400 --> 37:53.480
Your devotion to capturing
the murderer who killed your mother

37:53.480 --> 37:55.190
speaks volumes of your filial piety.

37:55.190 --> 37:56.590
This Phoenix Heart Token

37:57.110 --> 38:00.190
was originally left to Princess Yunzhao
by Empress Wenxi.

38:00.190 --> 38:01.720
Now that she's passed away,

38:03.070 --> 38:04.870
it's only right that you keep it.

38:09.710 --> 38:11.360
Thank you for your gracious kindness,
Your Majesty.

38:11.360 --> 38:13.760
Should the secrets of
the Phoenix Heart Token ever be uncovered,

38:13.760 --> 38:17.090
I'll present this token to our great Ye
without hesitation.

38:18.150 --> 38:19.280
What a good girl.

38:20.630 --> 38:23.630
From now on, come to the palace
more often with Yuanji.

38:25.590 --> 38:26.650
Yes, Your Majesty.

38:47.840 --> 38:48.550
Xiao Wuyi.

38:51.060 --> 38:52.360
You forced me to personally send

38:52.360 --> 38:53.690
my own sister to prison.

38:54.510 --> 38:55.770
She committed murder,

38:57.400 --> 38:59.440
and the victim was none other than
Xie Jiayu's mother.

38:59.440 --> 39:01.570
You know perfectly well why she did it.

39:02.920 --> 39:04.250
She did it to protect me.

39:04.630 --> 39:05.360
Protect you?

39:06.710 --> 39:09.480
You both live in fear of
Crown Prince Wenxi's return,

39:09.480 --> 39:10.320
but Crown Prince Wenxi

39:10.320 --> 39:12.230
died 20 years ago!

39:14.070 --> 39:16.190
If it weren't for Princess Yunzhao
saving Li Lejun with her medical skills,

39:16.190 --> 39:18.480
Li Lejun's condition would never
have improved,

39:18.480 --> 39:20.610
and she wouldn't have lived until now.

39:20.630 --> 39:22.630
And yet, because of a little suspicion,

39:22.630 --> 39:23.670
a fleeting fear,

39:23.670 --> 39:25.440
she could raise her blade against
the very person who saved her.

39:25.440 --> 39:27.570
Tell me, did Li Lejun do nothing wrong?

39:29.440 --> 39:30.640
Once she chose to act,

39:30.920 --> 39:32.670
she must bear the consequences.

39:32.670 --> 39:34.060
Li Yizhi, as the Regent,

39:34.880 --> 39:36.820
you're supposed to know right from wrong

39:36.820 --> 39:37.760
and where the line must be drawn!

39:37.760 --> 39:39.340
Right from wrong?

39:41.110 --> 39:42.550
Do you dare say that you helped Xie Jiayu

39:42.550 --> 39:44.210
without any selfish motives?

39:53.030 --> 39:54.440
How insolent of you.

39:54.920 --> 39:57.240
You know how much I couldn't bear
to part with Yaoyao.

39:57.240 --> 39:59.380
Now that you've driven my sister
into jail,

39:59.380 --> 40:01.630
you still expect me to continue
being friends with you

40:01.630 --> 40:03.360
and push forward with the reform together?

40:03.360 --> 40:04.800
No such easy bargain exists

40:04.800 --> 40:05.920
in this world!

40:06.280 --> 40:07.680
Your Highness Prince Qi!

40:10.070 --> 40:12.030
If you must find someone to blame

40:12.510 --> 40:14.170
to make yourself feel better,

40:15.360 --> 40:16.230
you can hate me.

40:16.670 --> 40:17.400
But Li Yizhi,

40:19.190 --> 40:22.390
you, too, rose from the ranks of
the displaced commoners.

40:23.030 --> 40:25.490
Since you've chosen to
sit in this position,

40:26.550 --> 40:28.150
you should have a more compassionate heart

40:28.150 --> 40:29.610
and broader aspirations.

40:30.590 --> 40:31.850
The road ahead is long.

40:32.960 --> 40:35.020
Do not let fear and desire consume you

40:36.070 --> 40:38.530
and make you forget
the path you once walked.

41:02.880 --> 41:04.080
Is Crown Prince Wenxi

41:06.480 --> 41:07.480
really dead?

41:16.630 --> 41:17.440
He's dead.

41:19.510 --> 41:20.480
He died long ago,

41:22.920 --> 41:24.400
and he'll never come back.
